cer)|Jacques d'Amboise]] |{{Birth date and age|1934|7|28}} |1954 |''[[Seven Brides for Seven Brothers]]'' (1954) |- |[[Jolene Brand]] |{{Birth date and age|1934|7|31}} |1958 | |- |[[Myrna Hansen]] |{{Birth date and age|1934|8|5}} |1953 |''[[Playgirl (film)|Playgirl]]'' (1954) and ''[[Francis in the Navy]]'' (1955) |- |[[Karen Sharpe]] |{{Birth date and age|1934|9|20}} |1952 |''[[The Sniper (1952 film)|The Sniper]]'' (1952, uncredited) and ''[[Mad at the World]]'' (1955) |- |[[Sophia Loren]] |{{Birth date and age|1934|9|20}} |1950 |''[[Quo Vadis (1951 film)|Quo Vadis]]'' (1951), ''[[The Pride and the Passion]]'' (1957), ''[[Desire Under the Elms]]'' (1958) and ''[[Houseboat (film)|Houseboat]]'' (1958) |- |[[Brigitte Bardot]] |{{Birth date and age|1934|9|28}} |1952 |''[[Act of Love (1953 film)|Act of Love]]'' (1953) |- |[[Meg Myles]] |{{Birth date and age|1934|11|14}} |1954 |''[[Dragnet (1954 film)|Dragnet]]'' (1954, uncredited) |- |[[Joanna Barnes]] |{{Birth date and age|1934|11|15}} |1958 |''[[Auntie Mame (film)|Auntie Mame]]'' (1958) and ''[[Spartacus (film)|Spartacus]]'' (1960) |- |[[Barry Coe]] |{{Birth date and age|1934|11|26}} |1955 | |- |[[Leslie Parrish]] |{{Birth date and age|1935|3|18}} |1955 | |- |[[Charles Grodin]] |{{Birth date and age|1935|4|21}} |1954 |''[[20,000 Leagues Under the Sea (1954 film)|20,000 Leagues Under the Sea]]'' (1954, uncredited) |- |[[Ruta Lee]] |{{Birth date and age|1935|5|30}} |1954 |''[[Seven Brides for Seven Brothers]]'' (1954), ''[[Funny Face]]'' (1957) and ''[[Witness for the Prosecution (1957 film)|Witness for the Prosecution]]'' (1957) |- |[[Andra Martin]] |{{Birth date and age|1935|7|15}} |1957 |''[[The Lady Takes a Flyer]]'' (1958) and ''[[Yellowstone Kelly]]'' (1959) |- |[[Diahann Carroll]] |{{Birth date and age|1935|7|17}} |1954 |''[[Carmen Jones (film)|Carmen Jones]]'' (1954) and ''[[Porgy and Bess (film)|Porgy and Bess]]'' (1959) |- |[[John Saxon]] |{{Birth date and age|1935|8|5}} |1953 | |- |[[Rosenda Monteros]] |{{Bir